        <h4>Save time with Zapier Automations</h4>
        </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>At Tracksy, we want to make your clinic admin simple.</p>
        <p>Face it, you don’t get paid for clinic administration, and data entry is often pointless and always time-consuming.  Therefore, we’ve decided to offer partners a list of time-saving Zapier automations specifically tailored for use in their clinics.</p>
        <p>For those not familiar, Zapier is an American company that specializes in web-based applications integration.  “The easiest way to automate your work.” is its home page slogan. You can actually create Zapier workflows on your own for free.  However, if you don't want to be bothered with the details, Tracksy's skilled Zapier developers can help you get the job done.</p>
        <p>Below we've provided a few examples, although anything is possible.</p>
        <p>We offer fixed price options, often $99 AUD or less, for common yet vital integration jobs.  Tell us what you need, and we will promptly deliver an accurate quote.</p>
